{
  "local_port": 52132,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the postings under SSC?",
  "response": "The **Staff Selection Commission (SSC)** conducts various examinations to recruit staff for different posts in the Government of India ministries, departments, and organizations. The postings under SSC vary based on the examination cleared. Here are the major exams conducted by SSC and the associated postings:\n\n### 1. **SSC Combined Graduate Level (CGL) Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for various Group B and Group C posts in government departments.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Assistant Audit Officer  \n- Assistant Accounts Officer  \n- Income Tax Inspector  \n- Central Excise Inspector  \n- Assistant Section Officer (ASO)  \n- Inspector (Central Bureau of Narcotics)  \n- Sub Inspector (Central Bureau of Investigation)  \n- Junior Statistical Officer  \n- Statistical Investigator  \n- Divisional Accountant  \n- Auditor  \n\n---\n\n### 2. **SSC Combined Higher Secondary Level (CHSL) Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for lower division clerical and data entry roles.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Lower Division Clerk (LDC)  \n- Junior Secretariat Assistant (JSA)  \n- Postal Assistant (PA)  \n- Sorting Assistant (SA)  \n- Data Entry Operator (DEO)  \n\n---\n\n### 3. **SSC Junior Engineer (JE) Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for engineering posts in various government departments.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Junior Engineer (Civil)  \n- Junior Engineer (Mechanical)  \n- Junior Engineer (Electrical)  \n\n---\n\n### 4. **SSC Multitasking (Non-Technical) (MTS) Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for non-technical, Group C posts.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Peon  \n- Daftary  \n- Jamadar  \n- Chowkidar  \n- Safaiwala  \n- Multi-Tasking Staff (MTS)  \n\n---\n\n### 5. **SSC Stenographer Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for stenographer roles.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Stenographer Grade C  \n- Stenographer Grade D  \n\n---\n\n### 6. **SSC Selection Post Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for specific vacancies in different departments.  \n**Postings vary based on departmental requirements.**  \n\n---\n\n### 7. **SSC Constable (GD) Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for constable roles in paramilitary forces.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Constable (General Duty) in CAPFs (CRPF, BSF, ITBP, CISF, SSB)  \n\n---\n\n### 8. **SSC Scientific Assistant Exam**  \nThis exam recruits candidates for scientific and technical roles.  \n**Postings include:**  \n- Scientific Assistant (various fields)  \n\n### Key Notes:  \n- The postings are **all-India** in nature, and candidates may be posted anywhere in the country based on the requirements of the department.  \n- The salary and perks vary depending on the **Pay Level** as per the 7th Central Pay Commission.  \n\nFor specific details about postings, candidates should refer to the official notifications released by SSC for each exam.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
